<script type="text/javascript">
    const variantName = "AI_in_Advanced_Search";
    const isABTestWithCookie = false;

    /* START: AB Test Homepage - AI tab for unauthenticated users. */
    const LDConsent = hasCookieConsentById("vagdYWLSXoC06v");
    /* END: AB Test Homepage - AI tab for unauthenticated users. */

    if (
        /* START: AB Test Homepage - AI tab for unauthenticated users. */
        !LDConsent ||
        /* END: AB Test Homepage - AI tab for unauthenticated users. */
        !variantName || isABTestWithCookie) { // AB test is not configured or started using cookie for storing variant
        localStorage.removeItem("ab-test");
        window.ABTestVariant = null;
    } else {
        setABTestVariant();
    }

    function setABTestVariant() {
        const abTestInDedicatedRoute = ["advanced search","search results list"];
        const currentRoute = "search results list";
        if (abTestInDedicatedRoute && !abTestInDedicatedRoute.includes(currentRoute)) {
            // AB test is not configured for current route
            return;
        }
        
        const setVariantInLocalStorage = () => {
            const variant = "0" || 0;

            localStorage.setItem("ab-test", JSON.stringify({
                variant: btoa(variant),
                name: btoa(variantName)
            }));

            window.ABTestVariant = variant;
        }

        let storedVariantInfo = localStorage.getItem("ab-test");

        if (storedVariantInfo) {
            storedVariantInfo = JSON.parse(storedVariantInfo);

            // If the AB test was switched to another one while it was still in progress, create a new variant from scratch
            if (atob(storedVariantInfo.name) !== variantName ) {
                setVariantInLocalStorage();
            } else {
                window.ABTestVariant = atob(storedVariantInfo.variant);
            }
        } else {
            setVariantInLocalStorage();
        }
    }

    // used for some of the AB tests
    // copied from resources\assets\js\scripts\ConsentManagementService.js
    function hasCookieConsentById(consentId) {
        let consentStatus = false;
        const consentSettings = window.localStorage.getItem("uc_settings") ?? false;
        const consentSettingsObj = JSON.parse(consentSettings);
        if (!consentSettings?.length) {
            return false;
        }
        const servicesAgreement = consentSettingsObj.services;
        if (servicesAgreement) {
            servicesAgreement.forEach((service)=> {
                if (service.id === consentId) {
                    consentStatus = service.status;
                }
            });
        }
        return consentStatus;
    }
</script>

<script>
    // copied from resources\assets\js\scripts\ConsentManagementService.js
    function hasCookieConsentById(consentId) {
        let consentStatus = false;
        const consentSettings = window.localStorage.getItem("uc_settings") ?? false;
        const consentSettingsObj = JSON.parse(consentSettings);

        if (!consentSettings?.length) {
            return false;
        }

        const servicesAgreement = consentSettingsObj.services;

        if (servicesAgreement) {
            servicesAgreement.forEach((service)=> {
                if (service.id === consentId) {
                    consentStatus = service.status;
                }
            });
        }

        return consentStatus;
    }

    const thirdPartyConsents = {
        "Adform": "H1dDqVjOjWX",
        "Criteo": "11R-YKeEF",
        "Datadog Real User Monitoring": "Xl0HIOViY",
        "DoubleClick Floodlight": "CImaKXy6rZvK7O",
        "Facebook Pixel": "ko1w5PpFl",
        "Gemius": "rycTeqVoOiZm",
        "Google Ads": "n7skyZn19M6nvV",
        "Google Analytics 4": "87JYasXPF",
        "Google Analytics Audiences": "Skr99EiujbX",
        "Google Optimize": "gkEBFID-V",
        "Google Tag Manager": "BJ59EidsWQ",
        "Hotjar": "S1kgcNo_j-m",
        "LaunchDarkly": "vagdYWLSXoC06v",
        "Microsoft Advertising": "BkeKqEjuoZQ",
        "RTB House": "B1Ayg5Es_s-X",
        "Taboola": "HkMucNoOjWX",
        "Thribee": "FvL_NO3n8HW24w",
        "Trackuity": "8VVc_EBx",
        "Usercentrics Consent Management Platform": "H1Vl5NidjWX",
        "immoweb profile-enrichment": "z_gw5obBSFk9O1"
    };

    const getConsentStatus = () => {
        let status = {};
        status.action = "onBeforePageLoad";
        status.event = "consent_status";

        Object.entries(thirdPartyConsents).forEach(entry => {
            const [key, value] = entry;
            status[key] = hasCookieConsentById(value);
        });

        window.dataLayer?.push(status);
    };

    // Universal Analytics event
    window.dataLayer.push(
        {
            "user": {
                "loginStatus": "logged out",
                "id": "",
                "personal": {
                    "language": ""
                }
            },
                                    "screen": {
                "name": "search results list",
                "language": "fr"
            }

        }
    );

    // Send third party consents status
    getConsentStatus();

    // Will be used to send the AB test variant
    let abTestVariantDescription = '';
    if (window.ABTestVariant !== undefined && window.ABTestVariant !== null) {
        abTestVariantsDescriptions = ["Version A - control: Only classic Advanced Search","Version B - variant: With AI in Advanced Search"];
        abTestVariantDescription = abTestVariantsDescriptions[window.ABTestVariant] ?? 'n/a';
    }

    /* START: AB Test - AI in Advanced Search. */
    const user = {};
    if (!user?.id) {
        abTestVariantDescription = '';
    }
